A 16% difference between my actual record and my all-play record feels non-trivial. In fact, in comparing that level of under-performance to the prior seasons (some of which we played with a ["superflex"](https://www.si.com/fantasy/2023/08/22/fantasy-football-101-what-is-superflex), contributing to more variance), I find that there were only 6 less fortunate outcomes, including a -29% difference for myself in 2020!




