The magnitude of the points will vary by league, according to the league's rules for roster slots and points. If your league is anything like mine, then you can expect to lose out on about 20 points due to about 2 sub-optimal starting roster choices each week.

Now, looking at the "lost opportunity" points compared to the league average for the past 6 seasons, we see that things tend to average out close to zero.




